ygData.messageBody:
About the Najena thing, once we have enough local players hitting 25, we can
go hunt down the mob with the Journey man boots liao. She conned black to me
for four spawns and her 2 side kick necros con blue to me and I was 25.
However that place is VERY camped, but I noticed that from 4-7pm, that place
quite empty. So I'm sure most ppl want boots cept those can SoW themselves,
therefore I suggest a Najena trip soon. (maybe can even get a few FBRs and
whips =)
btw, no need keys to open door, eye of zomm works just as well. Just have to
summon eye, then use the eyeball and push the door to open. Works for locked
doors as well. About the Staff, the eyeball is level 35 (Info from sereph)
and the oracle robe is also from a level 30+ mob in OOT.

Leshrec High Elven Wizard of the Seventh Circle.
